Q. Create new user 'cdac' on your local machine 'localhost'.

mysql> create user 'cdac'@'localhost' identified by 'cdac@123';

Q. Grant all priviliges of College databases' all tables to user 'cdac'

mysql> grant all on student.student to 'cdac'@'localhost';
Query OK, 0 rows affected (0.12 sec)

Q. Grant only select privilege to user on Sample database's EMP table.

mysql> grant select on sample.EMP to 'cdac'@'localhost';
Query OK, 0 rows affected (0.08 sec)

Q. Grant insert to user on Sample database's Dept table.

mysql> grant select, insert on sample.DEPT TO 'cdac'@'localhost';
Query OK, 0 rows affected (0.14 sec)

Q. Login to new User

diot@diot-HP-ProDesk-600-G5-PCI-MT:~$ mysql -u cdac -p
Enter password: 

Q. Try to insert a record in EMP table.

mysql> insert into EMP values(7944,'HOLDEN','ANALYST',7900,'1980-12-18','NULL','40');
ERROR 1142 (42000): INSERT command denied to user 'cdac'@'localhost' for table 'EMP'

Q. Try to select all dept records.

mysql> update DEPT set DNAME='ADVERTISING' where DNAME='RESEARCH';
ERROR 1142 (42000): UPDATE command denied to user 'cdac'@'localhost' for table 'DEPT'

Q. Drop user.

mysql> drop user 'cdac'@'localhost';
Query OK, 0 rows affected (0.12 sec)


Q. Remove all privileges given user 'cdac' on College database.

mysql> revoke all on student.student from 'cdac'@'localhost';
Query OK, 0 rows affected (0.11 sec)




